metadata.name: I healed over tea
metadata.description:
I pour myself another cup,
The only good thing I've been doing for myself.
It's small, it's kind,
It's better than pouring from my mind.
Tea doesn't ask questions, tea doesn't ridicule my mistakes.
Tea just listens, tea understands, 
And tea doesn't take.

-Marilyn D'cruz

This collaborative artwork by Ishleen and Marilyn is the reflection of a healing journey. Tea is an integral element and an artistic expression that flows through the work of both the creators. 

The artwork is an intersection of the magical journeys of growth, self love and empathy that brings these two artists together.
